{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-14408/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-14408"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:44:08"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["full shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man stands sadly in front behind his front door."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-14408","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-14408"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/canvas/1/a5241142-7993-45d9-bc4b-c81d28a089f2","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-07-02T23:51:50.487Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds is shot from a distance to convey his loneliness.&nbsp; He stands by the front door like a little boy or puppy awaiting Alma’s return. Although there’s no peephole on the door, he positions himself as in <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW191146528 BCX4\" href=\"https://digbmc.github.io/pt-annotated/items/phan-04252.html\"><u>this previous scene</u></a> when he watched Alma during the fashion show. Throughout the entire film, he has been trying to capture the effervescent Alma with his aesthetic vision, to somehow get her to freeze and become the object of his craft and desire.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-14408/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1112.6139530254777,312.3890326433121,217.9374004777069,471.4251592356687"}}}]}]}]}